ATEE LAA YO-JAAWE-ZO HUNNA BARROON WA LAA FAAJE-ROON FA-INNA-KA LAA TABEE-DO WA LAA TAN-FADO AN TO-SALLE-YA A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WA TA-QABBAL MINNEE WA MIN JAMEE-I’L MOMENEE-NA WAL MOMENAA-TE SEYAA-MA SHAHRE RAMAZAA-NA WA QEYAAMA-HU WA TA-FUKKA REQAA-BANAA MENAN NAARE. ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WAJ-A’L QALBEE BARRAN WA A’MALE SARRAN WA RIZQEE DAARAN WA HAWZA NABIYYE-KA A’LAIY-HE WA AALE-HIS SALAAMO LEE QARAA-RAN WA MUSTA-QARRAN WA TO-A’JJE-LA FARAJA AALE MOHAMMADIN FEE A’A-FEYA-TAN YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ اَسْئَلُكَ بِمَعَاقِدِ الْعِزِّ مِنْ عَرْشِكَ وَمُنْتَهَى الرَّحْمَةِ مِنْ كِتَابِكَ وَبِاسْمِكَ الْاَعْظَمِ وَكَلِمَاتِكَ التَّامَّةِ الَّتِيْ لَا يُجَاوِزُهُنَّ بَرٌّ وَلَا فَاجِرٌ فَاِنَّكَ لَا تَبِيْدُ وَلَا تَنْفَدُ اَنْ تُصَلِّيَ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَتَقَبَّلَ مِنِّيْ وَمِنْ جَمِيْعِ الْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ وَالْمُؤْمِنَاتِ صِيَامَ شَهْرِ رَمَضَانَ وَقِيَامَهٗ وَتَفُكَّ رِقَابَنَا مِنَ النَّارِ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَاجْعَلْ قَلْبِيْ بَارًّا وَعَمَلِي سَارًّا وَرِزْقِيْ دَارًّا وَحَوْضَ نَبِيِّكَ عَلَيْهِ وَآلِهِ السَّلَامُ لِيْ قَرَارًا وَمُسْتَقَرًّا وَتُعَجِّلَ فَرَجَ آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ فِيْ عَافِيَةٍ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "Ara